snippet.title: Simple FPS Aim Trainer - Trailer
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1421020/Simple_FPS_Aim_Trainer/



An FPS Aim Trainer for fast and lightweight target practice with built in game sensitivity conversion and matching, easily switch between popular games to match your mouse sensitivity
